data.description: Positioned on a prestigious corner lot, this meticulously crafted three-bedroom home epitomizes luxury living. The upgraded kitchen showcases granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious pantry for storage convenience. Inside, the master suite offers dual walk-in closets, a luxurious Roman tub, and a convenient step-in shower. Elegant tile flooring graces the living areas, while laminate flooring adds warmth to the bedrooms. Outside, a screened patio provides the perfect space for outdoor relaxation and family gatherings overlooking the lush private yard. Community amenities abound, including an Spacious 18,000sqft clubhouse, resort-style pool, state-of-the-art fitness center, 5 tennis courts, bocce, an array of lakes, miles of walking paths, and 2 pickleball courts. Strategically situated in close proximity to shopping centers, healthcare facilities, cultural attractions, the Turnpike, and major airports, this residence presents an epitome of upscale living in a highly sought-after locale, seamlessly blending luxury with unparalleled convenience and accessibility.
